1.1.1.1
log
@import garmindev: garmin gps device driver

pkg/DESCR:
Garmin GPS device driver plugins. They are no real device drivers, they
are just converting data into a bytestream on the USB or serial
interface and vice versa.

OK landry@@, jasper@@


